summary: The Power of Taylor Swift
title: The Power of Taylor Swift
body:
I believe now, that i have been a regular Swiftie for years now.. that the power that Taylor has over us is so strong and kinda like a “Good Power” ?? that She can make us do anything these days.


I mean if she says we should start saying hello to more people on the streets just to be nicer i would do it you know? 

If she says like, hey we should support this charity because “blablabla”, I WILL SUPPORT IT! 

It’s just crazy, i have my on head, do not be mistaken… if she told us to jump from a 30 floor building of course i wouldnt do it, but i know she will never asked us to do so… Cause she ‘s a nice person… The best one.

All this years seeing her under the spotlight, seeing every news in english and spanish talking about her… good stuff, bad stuff, good thing turned bad. Of course i have an opinion about it and i had talked with my friends, sister, cousins (Never online tho, i dont believe talking online is very nice, like sometimes y just put a heart or the 2 hands in the air, but never commented on real scale cause i think if i had 2 billion comments on how i look today i will feel so much pressure, so insecure about me) and it actually broke my heart when i saw so much news being mean?
Like i recieve so many comments that “Well she must be the witch, spoiled, brat person they say she is” and i’m like What?. She has been doing so many stuff, good stuff like supporting other women agains sexual assault, like givin money to sick-fans., etc.. i could go all day. And then i see or hear “She is just advertising her music by giving money away…it’s fake…If she wanted to donate money she could do it under the radar…” And im like WHAAAAT?


There are things I will never understand about how people love talking thrash about other people… and how we love? commenting bad thing of famous people? Cause what’s the point? If you dont like Taylor Swift FINE! don’t listen to her. Honestly it’s better for us “The Swifties” cause  we are so many already, Tours tickets sold out way to fast for me to handle. (And by the way I’m from Chile, so I’ve just seen the Shows online). It’s okay if you don’t like her, I don’t like Lana del Rey but you wont ever see me talking bad shit about her… cause she’s great.


So I really don’t know what i meant by writing this… but It’s 11AM already, and i felt like writing it.


Sorry for all the grammar mistakes and everything … but English is not my first language hehe.
